public class CommissionProgrammer extends Programmer
This class gathers gross sales and commission rate information of a programmer.
Author:
Nouraldin Hassan

  • Constructor Details

    • CommissionProgrammer

      public CommissionProgrammer(String firstName, String lastName, String socialSecurityNumber, int month, int year, double grossSales, double commissionRate)
      This constructor passes full name, SSN, month, year, gross sales, and commission rate of the programmer. full name and SSN is gathered from the superclass.
      Parameters:
      firstName - the first name of the programmer
      lastName - the last name of the programmer
      socialSecurityNumber - the SSN of the programmer
      month - the month of the programmer
      year - the year of the programmer
      grossSales - the gross weekly sales per hour of the programmer
      commissionRate - the commission rate percentage of the programmer
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - Commission rate must be > 0.0 and < 1.0
      IllegalArgumentException - Gross sales must be >= 0.0
